Class Consultation

java.lang.Object
es.mdef.mipediatralib.entities.Consultation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Reminder, Comparable<Reminder>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Emergency, RegularVisit
public class Consultation extends Object implements Reminder
Representa una consulta realizada por un especialista a un paciente en un centro médico.
